The paper focuses on incorporating security and privacy requirements into IoT application design, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). It also discusses design notations, models, and languages, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the need for different software and hardware to work together, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the complexities of IoT application development, which is related to cybernetics (cs.CY).
